<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sit-up">sit up</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>坐起来；坐直；熬夜：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If burns are on the face, the victim should sit up. 
如果脸部烧伤，伤员应该坐直。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We sat up late watching a movie. 
我们熬夜看了场电影。</p></div></div>